title: Mad Bytes It! 1996 CD
description:
Mad Bytes It!

From 1996, Mad Bytes It!, a CD included with MAD Magazine.
It includes a stupid index of what was in the first 35 years of Mad, some stupid covers and stupid posters and stupid songs and other stupid wastes of time.

Interesting  note: This did not work worth a hoot on any OS that was around in 1996, but it seems to work perfectly under Vista.  Go figure.  Maybe it's because of the picture of William E. Gates on the front of the CD.

-ekb-
